{
  "stem": "16059.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So now my parents attempted, once again, to try to emigrate to the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the immigration didn't like the looks of my lungs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just did not-- he said, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We cannot allow you to pass through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your daughter is not in good health.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the doctor had released me to go to school, to begin to take on a normal life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My parents kept going, and they said, we'll come back, come back, come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, they made a big issue of the scar tissue there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "With letters from the doctor, nothing helped for a long time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the meantime, my sister was born.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that caused more difficulty, because she needed papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so they waited and waited, which gave me a chance to heal and go to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think I had about a year and a half of school, that's all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And finally, they agreed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Immigration agreed to let me through with many more letters from the doctor assuring them that I was good enough and capable of going to the United States.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so in 1949, we took off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The HIAS organization helped us, H-I-A-S.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my mother's sister, Renee, and brother, Jack, who immigrated to Indianapolis, sponsored us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But of course, we went to-- we first went to Paris and then boarded a ship in Cannes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we went-- after Cannes, we went on to-- we boarded-- yeah, we boarded the ship.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was a grueling-- it was just a terrible trip.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was very, very ill, my mother and I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Seasickness is a-- ships at that time were not stabilized the way they are today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we ended up in New York, I believe in Manhattan at the HIAS organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had lodging and food for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
